1
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:19,280
Governor,

2
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:21,610
there's no need to thank me so much.

3
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,600
Wang Shiqi,

4
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:25,800
you really ruined my plans.

5
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:28,520
Your Guitou Sword can block illusions,

6
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:30,450
but it can't block bullets, can it?

7
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:33,080
You truly are a veteran of the battlefield.

8
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,800
To think of using pain

9
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,460
to break the illusion.

10
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,930
I never believe in ghosts and gods.

11
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,600
I only believe in myself.

12
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:42,440
So,

13
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:44,400
when that old bastard Song Ping

14
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,280
tried to fool me with the Paper Lady,

15
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:48,040
I pretty much guessed his goal.

16
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,000
So you decided to play along.

17
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:51,040
Exactly.

18
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:54,080
I also achieved military exploits.

19
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:56,520
I just wasn't as lucky as her

20
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:58,850
to have a Marshal for a brother.

21
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,060
Therefore,

22
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:02,200
I'm mocked by outsiders

23
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,680
for relying on my wife for promotion,

24
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:05,000
and swallow my pride at home.

25
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:05,760
Why should I?

26
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,260
I was indeed a bit willful.

27
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,400
But my heart was truly yours.

28
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,320
I have never let you down.

29
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,720
Even when I was caught by the Qing court

30
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:18,050
and severely tortured,

31
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,800
I never revealed your hiding place.

32
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,440
To think that time,

33
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,530
you managed to come back alive.

34
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,440
What a waste of my scheming.

35
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:31,400
You betrayed me.

36
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,680
You wanted me dead even back then.

37
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,610
If you don't die,

38
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:38,440
the heavy burden on me will never be lifted.

39
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:40,930
Originally,

40
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,600
I wanted to pretend to be bewitched,

41
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,320
so I could blame your death

42
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,360
entirely on Song Ping.

43
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,000
Then I'd kill that old bastard

44
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,000
to avenge you.

45
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,170
Gaining both fame and fortune.

46
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,400
How perfect.

47
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,039
As a result,

48
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,480
you ruined my plan once again.

49
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,200
So I have to do it myself.

50
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,140
If you actually shoot,

51
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,600
you'll truly be doomed.

52
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,039
Turn back now,

53
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,060
and I might still forgive you.

54
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,200
I don't need anyone's forgiveness.

55
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,000
I just want to get everything I desire.

56
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,680
And you

57
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,280
are next.

58
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,200
No bullets.

59
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,800
Your bullets

60
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,680
are right here.

61
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,100
Snitching a few things

62
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,860
is still a piece of cake for me.

63
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,880
Didn't expect me to come here, did you?

64
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:42,210
I also snagged some stuff while I was at it.

65
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,600
You are smart.

66
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,660
You owe me big time again for this.

67
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,880
Do you still not believe Wang Shiqi even now?

68
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,010
Then let me tell you,

69
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,770
you will believe him very soon.

70
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,080
This medicine

71
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,800
can break illusions.

72
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,700
These are my personal guards.

73
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,450
They only follow my orders.

74
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,930
Even if you made preparations,

75
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,440
what exactly happened tonight

76
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,320
is still up to me to decide.

77
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:27,800
Adjutant,

78
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:28,960
bring me a gun.

79
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,400
Madam.

80
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,600
What should we do with this bastard?

81
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,000
You...

82
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,480
How dare you betray me!

83
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,600
We were never your men.

84
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,329
We only answer to Madam.

85
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,280
Shiqi,

86
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,660
it's time you learned something new.

87
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,560
Madam,

88
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,640
for the sake of our marriage,

89
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:07,570
please spare me.

90
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,480
Please.

91
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,880
You think...

92
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,529
If it weren't for me,

93
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,380
would a single soldier

94
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,040
listen to your orders?

95
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,240
Madam,

96
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,090
you're here.

97
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,920
Leaving in such a hurry,

98
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,360
you didn't even wait for me.

99
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,520
Do you have a death wish?

100
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:36,880
Madam.

101
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,720
Seven years.

102
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,450
I didn't expect it was all fake.

103
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,440
Don't catch a cold.

104
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,440
You don't deserve my tears anymore.

105
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,480
Well?

106
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,580
Now that the commander's seat is vacant,

107
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,730
are you interested?

108
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:56,640
Madam,

109
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,840
I'm just an executioner.

110
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,340
I'm not fit to lead troops.

111
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:00,860
Perhaps

112
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,660
the commander's position

113
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,730
really is more suitable for me.

114
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,210
However,

115
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:19,080
you can come to me anytime you figure it out,

116
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,410
but you need to be quick.

117
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,520
Maybe

118
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,200
I'll fancy someone else one day.

119
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,360
This is another lesson I'm teaching you

120
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,600
on how to handle men.

121
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,159
Women sometimes

122
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,000
need to take the initiative.

123
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,450
Let's go.

124
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,400
So this is what it feels like to be kissed by a woman.

125
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,130
Who's there?

126
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,170
Come with me.

127
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,400
You mean that guy Song Ping?

128
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,080
He was in prison,

129
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,440
and suddenly disappeared.

130
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,240
The guards on duty know nothing.

131
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,680
It's really strange.

132
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,659
The Nine Chrysanthemum Faction,

133
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,260
Japanese warlocks who cut dragon veins.

134
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,600
Song Ping

135
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,340
was also in cahoots with them.

136
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:46,640
But,

137
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:49,200
Taohua Town is no longer under his control.

138
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,960
Without this obstacle,

139
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,920
peaceful days in Taohua Town

140
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,360
will soon arrive.

141
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,600
But I always feel that

142
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,600
the truth behind the Song family's matter

143
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,660
is not that simple.

144
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,060
Our top priority is to find him first.

145
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,780
And think about it.

146
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,360
Even if he is cold-blooded,

147
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,160
he couldn't have killed so many people

148
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,290
just for an antique.

149
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:11,760
Mayor,

150
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,240
look.

151
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Why have all the flowers withered this season?

152
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,800
Yeah.

153
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,720
When my flowers bloom,

154
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,860
all others perish.

155
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,440
Regarding Song Ping's disappearance,

156
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,170
we have news.

157
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,180
Why bring up Song Ping?

158
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:34,840
Will you marry me?

159
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,159
Even though

160
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,260
I don't hate you as much as before,

161
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:43,000
the situation in Taohua Town is still unstable.

162
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,730
I need to stay with my father to manage this place.

163
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,600
It's the same for you.

164
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,920
You should stay

165
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,280
and use your skills,

166
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,960
instead of spending every day

167
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,680
thinking only about romance.

168
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,360
So that's a no.

169
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,000
Brother Wang!

170
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,440
Brother Wang!

171
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,200
He isn't angry, is he?

172
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:06,520
But,

173
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,120
Miss Su,

174
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,120
there is something I really want to tell you.

175
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,800
If I were you,

176
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,660
I would have married him long ago.

177
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:12,920
Wanrong,

178
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,890
you can't really be indifferent, can you?

179
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:16,960
Yeah.

180
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,400
Oh my.

181
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,040
This stone has been here for over a hundred years,

182
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,440
always used to ward off evil,

183
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:29,720
and it represents the peace of our Taohua Town.

184
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,400
My brother,

185
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,000
even if he's angry

186
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,080
about the rejected proposal,

187
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,740
he shouldn't be so impulsive.

188
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,640
I say, Miss Su,

189
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,080
why don't you just marry him?

190
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,679
Yeah.

191
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,120
What's going on?

192
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,260
What's happening?

193
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,040
Blood!

194
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,920
There's blood!

195
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,580
Blood here!

196
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,330
Bodhisattva, please bless us.

197
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,840
Bless our Taohua Town.

198
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,930
Bless us with good weather.

199
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,250
When Chief Song was around,

200
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,880
although he was overbearing,

201
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,480
at least

202
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,800
the town was peaceful,

203
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,460
without so many weird things.

204
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,360
Now,

205
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:17,280
even the evil-warding stele at the town hall has cracked.

206
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,600
The stele has cracked.

207
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:22,640
That's because the Song family's ancestors were high-ranking officials.

208
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,500
Their spirits linger after death

209
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,520
and have always protected Taohua Town.

210
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,800
Otherwise, how could Song Ping

211
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,520
vanish without a trace?

212
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,120
Exactly.

213
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:32,840
Look at us now.

214
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,610
Taking down the Song family

215
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,480
has angered their ancestors.

216
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,520
It's retribution.

217
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:41,660
If we had known,

218
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,600
we'd be better off with Song Ping in charge of Taohua Town.

219
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,440
Exactly.

220
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,080
Yeah.

221
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,680
Let us in.

222
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,620
Move aside.

223
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,600
Quiet down, everyone.

224
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,330
Listen to me.

225
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:00,000
This is just a rare weather phenomenon.

226
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,080
It's not a heavenly tribulation,

227
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,160
nor an evil omen,

228
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,120
let alone the Song family ancestors manifesting.

229
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,520
There is no need to panic.

230
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,640
That's easy for you to say.

231
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,240
Then how do you explain all the things

232
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,040
that happened in town recently?

233
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:09,880
Yeah, exactly.

234
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,520
Even Wang Shiqi isn't showing up to solve this.

235
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,240
It means this time,

236
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,360
it must be the will of heaven.

237
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,760
Right.

238
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,620
We will look into the details.

239
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,640
Everyone, go back first.

240
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:19,100
We'll give you an answer as soon as possible.

241
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:19,880
Let's all go back.

242
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,440
Go back.

243
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,770
Everyone, listen to me.

244
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,800
Everyone, just head back first.

245
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:26,000
We will give you a satisfactory answer.

246
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:26,840
Let's all go back.

247
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,680
Go back.

248
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,000
Take everyone back first.

249
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,080
I'll go check the situation with Captain Jia.

250
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,600
Alright.

251
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,530
Come on, everyone, follow me back.

252
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,080
The Song family's ancestral tomb

253
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,740
is the largest in Taohua Town.

254
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,040
Wang Shiqi.

255
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,520
Wang Shiqi.

256
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,640
Although Song Ping is hateful,

257
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,800
this grave-digging is really inappropriate.

258
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,480
And now,

259
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,120
the villagers are all talking about it.

260
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,080
It will affect public sentiment.

261
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,840
Yeah.

262
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,400
If you really want to marry me,

263
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,660
you shouldn't be so...

264
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,600
Where did the bones inside go?

265
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:09,800
This...
